data.description: Welcome to your coastal oasis in Snead's Ferry, NC! This charming two-story, 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. The master suite is a true retreat, featuring a spacious bedroom with a trey ceiling, a luxurious master bathroom with elegant tile flooring and surrounds, and an oversized soaking tub for ultimate relaxation. In all bathrooms, you'll find exquisite, brushed nickel fixtures that add a touch of refinement to every space. The master suite also boasts a generous walk-in closet, providing ample space for your wardrobe. The home also offers a modern, open kitchen with stainless steel appliances, a breakfast bar, and an inviting living room, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere, perfect for both entertaining and relaxation. In addition, a large two-car garage with built-in expansive storage shelving is a fantastic addition for organizing and maintaining your belongings. Outside, you'll appreciate the low-maintenance fenced-in backyard, making outdoor living a breeze. The covered patio with a ceiling fan provides an excellent space for relaxation and entertainment. The large covered front porch is perfect for sipping your morning coffee or chatting with neighbors. For outdoor enthusiasts and those who love serene views, this property is conveniently located within walking distance of a community pond. It's a tranquil spot for relaxation and outdoor activities. Located in close proximity to Intracoastal boat launches, beautiful beaches, and Stone Bay, this property provides the perfect combination of comfort and coastal convenience. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to make Snead's Ferry your new home, where luxury, practicality, and coastal charm come together seamlessly. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and make this coastal retreat, with its stunning master suite, modern kitchen, spacious garage, and outdoor amenities, yours!
